00:35:58.180 --> 00:36:00.620
[laughter]
So this might be the most fun you can have

00:36:00.620 --> 00:36:08.440
with a pig, legally. [loud laughter] These
areó[laughs] These are some shots on the

00:36:08.440 --> 00:36:12.370
way to taking this shot, which is one of my
